&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;GTN Graph transformer network&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;RSHN  Relation structure-aware heterogeneous graph neural network&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;HetGNN heterogeneous graph neural network（这个算法还是很优秀的，感觉，思路很清楚）&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;MAGNN meta-path aggregate graph neural network，HAN 的加强版。&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;HGT heterogeneous graph transformer&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;HetSANN Attention-based graph neural network for heterogeneous structural learning (这个算法细节没有给出）&lt;/li&gt;
